TextBody:
Hi Mihai,

Thank you for your email.
For the time being, please disregard the hotfix 1.1 that does not go away even after being applied.
If you applied it, even one/multilple times and it shows under Live Update-View applied EPP Software Updates,
you can disregard the lingering update. That will eventually go away after the new server version will be released.

In organizatie avem instalat clientul 5.3.7.0 .
Ieri am downloadat 6.2.2.1 si l-am distribuit prin SCCM.
Dupa ce s-a distribuit si instalat, calculatoarele au inceput sa aiba probleme la autentificare. Nu mai reuseau duca la capat autentificarea, calculatoarele ramaneau in ecran negru, clientul le bloca acest lucru.
Am retras de pe statii clientul 6.2.2.1 si am revenit la 5.3.7.0, acum totul este in regula.
Ati mai intampinati situatia asta si la alti clienti ?
Subject: Netwrix Support Ticket #414446 - Live Update
